## Frontend (React 19)
- Functional components only — no class components
- Custom hooks for reusable logic (use* prefix)
- TypeScript: strict mode, typed props interface
- State: useState for local, useReducer for complex, React Query for server state
- No prop drilling beyond 2 levels — use context or React Query
- CSS variables for theming — never hardcoded color values
- Lazy loading: React.lazy() + Suspense for route-level code splitting
